l = lookup.TemplateLookup()
l.put_string('foo.html',
    """
            <%def name="foo()">
            </%def>
        """)
l.put_string('bar.html',
    """
        <%namespace name="foo" file="foo.html"/>

        ${foo.notfoo()}
        """
    )
self.assertRaises(AttributeError, l.get_template('bar.html').render)
